      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-tucked and spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
