    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in immaculate condition. This S54-powered masterpiece features individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling, with a meticulously documented service history confirming rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis is structurally superior, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Power is managed via a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit stability. The exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. A mechanically peerless example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
