    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece, preserved in what can only be described as showroom-floor condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from any swirls, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and a recent professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of creasing or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting meticulous maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or debris. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Truly a turn-key investment for someone who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
